01:17:06.055 --> 01:17:08.224
I wish I could
share them too."

01:17:09.592 --> 01:17:11.127
It's beautiful.

01:17:11.160 --> 01:17:12.528
Really?
Yeah.

01:17:12.561 --> 01:17:14.163
(Kyle crying)
MARGARET: Shh.

01:17:19.736 --> 01:17:21.404
