I stopped taking showers.

01:19:14.784 --> 01:19:16.452
My mom would say,

01:19:16.485 --> 01:19:19.255
"Why do you want to treat your
body with such disrespect?"

01:19:19.288 --> 01:19:21.424
I had no idea why.

01:19:21.457 --> 01:19:23.226
But now I do.

01:19:25.728 --> 01:19:27.663
You probably thought
I forgot,

01:19:27.696 --> 01:19:30.867
but I remember everything
you did to me.

01:19:30.900 --> 01:19:33.970
Sometimes I thought
maybe you forgot.

01:19:34.003 --> 01:19:37.874
But you were a grown man
at the time you molested me.

01:19:39.608 --> 01:19:41.710
If you are a Christian,

01:19:41.744 --> 01:19:43.479
and I think you are,

01:19:43.512 --> 01:19:45.481
then you know
what awaits you.

01:19:46.883 --> 01:19:51.154
Yours truly,
little Katie next door.

01:20:07.203 --> 01:20:08.604
Katie.

01:20:08.637 --> 01:20:09.772
Miss Matsuo.

01:20:09.805 --> 01:20:11.807
How's the grand
experiment?

01:20:11.841 --> 01:20:13.776
Excuse me?

01:20:13.809 --> 01:20:15.611
Life without semesters?

01:20:15.644 --> 01:20:18.047
Oh, it's great.

01:20:18.081 --> 01:20:19.182
Good.

01:20:20.583 --> 01:20:22.718
Actually,
I just lied to you.

01:20:22.751 --> 01:20:25.021
It's really,
really hard.

01:20:27.323 --> 01:20:28.591
I'm sorry.

01:20:30.259 --> 01:20:31.460
That's okay.

01:20:31.494 --> 01:20:33.596
You know, I--
I think it's getting better.

01:20:33.629 --> 01:20:36.265
I think I'm going
to be okay.

01:20:36.299 --> 01:20:38.134
Well, you take care.

01:20:41.404 --> 01:20:43.272
* Did you hear

01:20:43.306 --> 01:20:46.675
* Where I was going,
