01:20:46.709 --> 01:20:48.844
* Did you see me

01:20:48.878 --> 01:20:52.882
* Walking down that road?

01:20:54.483 --> 01:20:57.153
* And do you understand

01:20:57.186 --> 01:21:00.523
* That my life
(Unclear)

01:21:00.556 --> 01:21:02.892
* And no, baby

01:21:02.926 --> 01:21:05.028
* You know I'm not
very old

01:21:05.061 --> 01:21:08.731
Well, if it isn't one of my
favourite people in the world.

01:21:08.764 --> 01:21:10.967
That's me.

01:21:12.035 --> 01:21:13.937
What's wrong?

01:21:14.938 --> 01:21:16.805
Just wanted
to come say hi.

01:21:16.839 --> 01:21:18.841
I don't believe that.

01:21:18.874 --> 01:21:21.610
Come on in. Tell me
what's going on with you.

01:21:27.083 --> 01:21:28.985
I need some advice.

01:21:30.486 --> 01:21:32.288
Okay.

01:21:35.024 --> 01:21:38.261
But I want to talk to you
about something first.

01:21:41.397 --> 01:21:44.800
I didn't quit
for the reason I said.

01:21:44.833 --> 01:21:48.504
My mom's fiancÃ© found out that
you're a convicted sex offender.

01:21:52.508 --> 01:21:54.944
That occurred to me.

01:22:00.616 --> 01:22:02.351
I wanted to tell you
the truth,

01:22:02.385 --> 01:22:05.554
but my mom would have grounded
me until the end of time.

01:22:05.588 --> 01:22:07.690
She was afraid for you.

01:22:07.723 --> 01:22:10.493
Well, hello, I'm a girl.

01:22:10.526 --> 01:22:12.495
But you're here now.

01:22:14.430 --> 01:22:16.399
What changed?

01:22:17.733 --> 01:22:19.335
I need your wisdom.

01:22:20.436 --> 01:22:23.006
But I want to know
what your crime was.

01:22:25.641 --> 01:22:26.976
Why?

01:22:27.010 --> 01:22:29.378
I need to know.

01:22:36.485 --> 01:22:38.721
(Glenn sighing)

01:22:38.754 --> 01:22:40.456
It was a long time ago.

01:22:43.392 --> 01:22:45.528
Please?

01:22:45.561 --> 01:22:47.096
(Exhaling)

01:22:48.197 --> 01:22:49.598
May I have one of those?

01:22:52.635 --> 01:22:54.037
You smoke?

01:22:54.070 --> 01:22:56.972
I'm what is known
in Nicotine Anonymous

01:22:57.006 --> 01:22:58.907
as a periodic.

01:22:58.941 --> 01:23:00.476
I start and stop.

01:23:02.545 --> 01:23:04.447
Right now I'm undecided.

01:23:04.480 --> 01:23:06.215
Have a seat.

01:23:11.587 --> 01:23:13.056
Ah, there it is.

01:23:14.790 --> 01:23:16.825
(Sniffing)

01:23:16.859 --> 01:23:18.361
(Sighing)

01:23:20.496 --> 01:23:22.065
Where do I begin?

01:23:25.968 --> 01:23:27.636
When I was
your age, Katie,

01:23:27.670 --> 01:23:30.439
I was a very angry,

01:23:30.473 --> 01:23:33.008
nasty piece of work.

01:23:33.042 --> 01:23:35.144
I was rarely
clean or sober.

01:23:35.178 --> 01:23:36.912
I had hair down to here
and a full beard,

01:23:36.945 --> 01:23:38.581
believe it or not.

01:23:38.614 --> 01:23:42.351
And when I was 19 years old
I got busted for selling drugs.

01:23:42.385 --> 01:23:47.090
So in order to avoid jail time
I enlisted in the Army.

01:23:47.123 --> 01:23:49.458
And I just stayed high
all the time.

01:23:49.492 --> 01:23:51.894
Well, surprise, surprise,
I get busted

01:23:51.927 --> 01:23:54.397
and dishonourably discharged
and sent home.

01:23:54.430 --> 01:23:57.966
And I stayed out of trouble
for a very long time,

01:23:58.000 --> 01:23:59.968
until one night
I got shit-face drunk

01:24:00.002 --> 01:24:03.272
and showed up at the house
of a woman I knew

01:24:03.306 --> 01:24:04.840
who was a prostitute.

01:24:04.873 --> 01:24:06.209
Not one that I could afford,

01:24:06.242 --> 01:24:09.312
but she had a soft spot
for vets.

01:24:09.345 --> 01:24:11.114
And the last thing
I remember was,

01:24:11.147 --> 01:24:14.917
she pulled out a bottle of rum
and a tab of acid.

01:24:14.950 --> 01:24:17.253
So when I woke up
in jail the next morning,

01:24:17.286 --> 01:24:19.855
I had no choice but to take her
word for what happened.

01:24:19.888 --> 01:24:24.493
And the word of the emergency
room doctor, of course.

01:24:24.527 --> 01:24:25.994
(Sighing)

01:24:26.028 --> 01:24:30.499
I did not rape her
in the way

01:24:30.533 --> 01:24:32.668
that most people
would define that term,

01:24:32.701 --> 01:24:35.604
but it was a very, uh,

01:24:35.638 --> 01:24:38.607
cruel sexual assault,

01:24:38.641 --> 01:24:40.476
and I paid the price.

01:24:45.248 --> 01:24:50.219
Now, tell me
what's wrong with you.

01:24:50.253 --> 01:24:52.521
I'm pregnant.

01:24:57.793 --> 01:25:00.229
Hmm.

01:25:00.263 --> 01:25:03.166
KATIE:
I'm just-- I'm too young
to have a baby.

01:25:03.199 --> 01:25:06.802
And I know-- I know I should
get an abortion.

01:25:06.835 --> 01:25:09.572
But days keep passing by,

01:25:09.605 --> 01:25:11.374
and I don't make
the appointment.

01:25:11.407 --> 01:25:12.875
(Sighing)

01:25:14.343 --> 01:25:18.747
I just-- I think I'm scared
to go alone.

01:25:18.781 --> 01:25:20.649
I think it's more
than that.

01:25:23.552 --> 01:25:26.121
I think you're afraid
to go at all.

01:25:26.155 --> 01:25:28.123
And for good reason.

01:25:28.157 --> 01:25:31.327
Because if you do this,

01:25:31.360 --> 01:25:35.331
there's no telling how
you'll feel about it later.

01:25:35.364 --> 01:25:38.000
You're afraid
you'll regret it.

01:25:38.033 --> 01:25:40.369
Maybe.

01:25:42.771 --> 01:25:46.509
But, you know,
very few people

01:25:46.542 --> 01:25:49.378
ever regret
having had a child.

01:25:50.979 --> 01:25:52.648
Is that true?
Absolutely.

01:25:54.082 --> 01:25:56.952
You want some more wisdom?
No extra charge.

01:25:56.985 --> 01:25:58.954
Please.

01:25:58.987 --> 01:26:01.690
Stop drinking
and smoking immediately.

01:26:01.724 --> 01:26:05.861
And you must never see
any of these men ever again.

01:26:05.894 --> 01:26:07.730
Dump Paul?

01:26:07.763 --> 01:26:09.498
No, no, he'll freak out.

01:26:09.532 --> 01:26:11.300
