listen to me.

01:26:11.334 --> 01:26:14.237
When a married man

01:26:14.270 --> 01:26:17.306
is having an affair
with a beautiful, young girl,

01:26:17.340 --> 01:26:18.707
no matter how much
he feels for that girl,

01:26:18.741 --> 01:26:20.543
he's always relieved
when it's over

01:26:20.576 --> 01:26:23.512
because he knows he's been
playing a dangerous game,

01:26:23.546 --> 01:26:26.382
and he's lucky
to escape alive.

01:26:28.884 --> 01:26:30.653
He doesn't love me?

01:26:30.686 --> 01:26:33.055
Not the way you think.

01:26:33.088 --> 01:26:35.090
But if I dump Paul,

01:26:35.123 --> 01:26:37.560
then I lose my job.

01:26:40.696 --> 01:26:44.400
Well, you could always
come back and work here.

01:26:44.433 --> 01:26:47.169
Yeah, my mom
would kill me.

01:26:47.202 --> 01:26:49.605
You don't need
her permission anymore.

01:26:49.638 --> 01:26:50.706
You're an adult.

01:26:50.739 --> 01:26:52.174
She'd kick me out
of the house--

01:26:52.207 --> 01:26:54.243
You know what?
There just happens to be

01:26:54.277 --> 01:26:56.445
an empty room
above my garage,

01:26:56.479 --> 01:26:58.414
and you're welcome to it,
rent-free.

01:27:00.583 --> 01:27:04.219
You have to start making
your own decisions, young lady.

01:27:04.253 --> 01:27:05.954
Now, come on.
I got to close up.

01:27:05.988 --> 01:27:07.390
