to be famous,

01:27:36.685 --> 01:27:38.186
even though we're not good
at anything.

01:27:38.220 --> 01:27:39.555
Precisely.

01:27:39.588 --> 01:27:41.624
You sure I can't
give you a lift?

01:27:41.657 --> 01:27:43.792
I like to walk.

01:27:43.826 --> 01:27:45.794
All right, then.

01:27:48.931 --> 01:27:50.433
