to be a mother.

01:28:22.230 --> 01:28:25.200
But have the baby anyway.

01:28:25.233 --> 01:28:27.035
What's the harm?

01:28:29.204 --> 01:28:32.575
I'll raise it as my own, and you
can come and go as you please.

01:28:32.608 --> 01:28:35.744
You can be as much of a mother
as you care to be.

01:28:43.285 --> 01:28:45.087
(Car alarm chirping)

01:28:48.156 --> 01:28:50.859
If I don't do
what you want me to,

01:28:50.893 --> 01:28:54.096
